	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S. D.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuas accepi et non sine dolore legi de extrema illa vestrorum corruptione.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non impune contemnetur semper deus neque feret diutius conscelerationem hanc.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim scimus deum non velle mortem peccatoris, sed magis ut convertatur et vivat; unde nobis laborandum fideli annunciatione verbi divini, si forte pro nostro officio multos possimus eripere ex hoc incendio et ad refrigerium aeternae vitae perducere.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ideo enim dominus vult, ut praedicatio evangelii eius ante ultimum adventum eius ubique annuncietur, certe pluribus ad iudicium.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l808" cert="high">Belgio</placeName> ne verbum quidem habemus.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Negat et pernegat <persName type="auto_name">Angusola</persName> verum esse, quod pro vero scribitur ex multis <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l822" cert="high">Germaniae</placeName> urbibus pugnatum esse 12. novembris clademque accepisse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875" cert="high">Hispanos</placeName>.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallia</placeName> quoque nihil habemus comperti.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribitur <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l41" cert="high">Berna</placeName> capitaneum <placeName cert="high" type="citizen_name" ref="l160">Friburgensem</placeName> a Berroman ex castris <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l160" cert="high">Friburgensibus</placeName> senatui scripsisse <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Gallos</placeName> conflixisse pugna velitari; sed <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">Helvetios</placeName> stetisse in acie neque quicquam damni vel dedisse vel accepisse.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Audimus alias regem cum suis copiis retrocedere <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l378" cert="high">Lutetiam</placeName>, pertinaciter autem sequi copias regias milites <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8315" cert="high">Condeanos</persName> nec ullam regiis permittere quietem.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l631" cert="high">Burgundi</placeName> metuentes ingentes <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l367" cert="high">Auranii</placeName> copias in <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> irrumpentes facultates suas, quas possunt, subvehunt <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l339" cert="high">Neoburgum</placeName> (Nüwenburg, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l339" cert="high">Neocomum</placeName>) et in vicina <placeName ref="l41" cert="high">Bernatum</placeName> loca et his credunt abscondendas.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miseranda est rerum facies.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Annon putas, mi frater, <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l832" cert="high">Galliam</placeName> tot tantisque hostium et amicorum copiis frustillatim discerpendam?</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hoc est dei saeverum, sed iustum iudicium.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dominus misereatur omnium nostrum et inducat in veram sui cognitionem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="farewell">Vale.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName> 21. ianuarii 1569.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingerus</persName> s[enior].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="19" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ornatissimo viro d. <persName ref="p8016" cert="high">Tobiae Eglio</persName>, <placeName ref="l98" cert="high">Curiensis</placeName> ecclesiae fideli ministro, domino colendo et fratri charissimo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="20" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Chur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note>[Dem Brief hat <persName ref="p4679" cert="high">Egli</persName> (zu Handen <persName ref="p6130" cert="high">Pontisellas</persName>?) auf der Vorderseite unten folgende Bemerkung beigefügt:]</note>
					<s n="21" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Iussus <persName type="auto_name">Raphael</persName> meus, ut <persName type="auto_name">Donatum</persName> ac partes orationis, quas pene oblivioni dedit, diligenter regustaret, causatus nescio quid negotii apud matrem statim extra aedes se proripuit ac concursavit per plateas pro more, quem verberibus productis, quaeso, iuves dedocere.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
